	* [r5886] *) Now octopus is also aware of the 1D exchange
	  functional
	  *) Replaced the _init_exchanged and _init_correlation by a
	  simpler
	  _init_functl
	  *) Some more tests are passed in 4D. The exceptions are now the
	  open
