	* [r6090] This fixes the 03-extended_eigenstate test when running
	  in 4D. The
	  problem was the use of "w" in the inp file, which collided with
	  the "w"
	  coordinate in 4D. Please DO NOT USE SINGLE LETTER VARIABLES IN
	  THE INPUT
	  FILE!

