2010-08-17 07:14  juho

	* [r6938] Wrong sign (the equation is solvable down to -1), wrong
	  return value. Returning zero gives us an effective lda
	  approximation. See PRB 76, 235314, page 4.

2010-08-17 17:57  dstrubbe

