	* [r6954] Added profiling regions to the dense hermitian
	  eigensolvers.

2010-08-23 10:45  xavier

	* [r6955] An array in partition_build was blowing up the memory for
	  large
	  parallel calculations.

2010-08-24 09:53  xavier

