2010-12-12 20:33  acastro

	* [r7166] Removed the diagonalization, by LAPACK, of one matrix
	  used in some
	  coordinate transformation in the QOCT code. Instead, the
	  eigenvectors
	  and eigenvalues are explicitly defined, because they can be
	  computed
	  analytically.

