	* [r7422] * The default orthogonalizer for states parallelization
	  is now
	  par_gram_schmidt.
	  
	  * Added checks for the selection of the orthogonalizer.
	  
	  * Improved the documentation for SubspaceDiagonalization and
	  StatesOrthogonalization.

